Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update Our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify You of any changes by posting the
                new Privacy Policy on this page.
If we make a material change to this policy that affects the collection and use of your personal
                information, We will let You know via a prominent notice on Our Service, prior to the change becoming
                effective and update the "Last updated" date at the top of this Privacy Policy. If we have your contact
                details we will notify you by email prior to making the change.
You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy
                are effective when they are posted on this page.
